## Populations This Platform Serves (Reference)

When writing scenarios, test descriptions, or documentation, draw from
these real threat contexts:

- Sex workers facing FOSTA-SESTA financial deplatforming
- IPV survivors whose partners have installed stalkerware on shared devices
- Activists organizing under authoritarian surveillance regimes
- Journalists carrying sensitive sources across hostile border crossings
- LGBTQ+ individuals in regions where "outing" carries physical danger
- People escaping coerced debt and financial abuse

These are not hypotheticals. They are the people the tests protect.
